tests.title: SEARCH_SPEC: All Sole - Return At Least 1 Item
tests.fullTitle: ==================== THG_IOS_PAGINATION: All Sole ==================== SEARCH_SPEC: All Sole - Return At Least 1 Item
tests.code:
function sectionsClick(done) {
var tries = 0;
function actualSearchTest(next) {
driver.chain()
.get(site.urls.live)
.elementByCss('.search-focus', function touchSearch(err, search) {
if (err) throw err;
search.flick(1, 1, 0, function flickCb(err) {
if (err) throw err;
driver.elementByCss('#search-text', 10000, function (err, el) {
el.sendKeys(wd.SPECIAL_KEYS.Return);
});
})
})
.waitForElementByCss('.item', 20000, function elementCb(err, el) {
if (err) throw err;
should.exist(el);
})
.title(function (err, title) {
if (title.indexOf(site.keys.searchFound) == -1) {
return next('Title not match');
}
return next(err);
})
}
function searchTest() {
try {
actualSearchTest(function (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold) {
searchTest();
}
else {
return done(err);
}
});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
searchTest();
else return done(err);
}
}
searchTest();

})
.waitForElementByCss('.item', 20000, function elementCb(err, el) {

})

return next(err);

try {

if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold) {
searchTest();
}
else {
return done(err);
}
});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
searchTest();
else return done(err);
}
}
searchTest();

searchTest();
}
else {
return done(err);

});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
searchTest();
else return done(err);
}
}

if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold) {
searchTest();
}
else {

});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
searchTest();
else return done(err);
}
}

var tries = 0;
function actualSearchTest(next) {
driver.chain()
.get(site.urls.live)
.elementByCss('.search-focus', function touchSearch(err, search) {
if (err) throw err;
search.flick(1, 1, 0, function flickCb(err) {
if (err) throw err;
driver.elementByCss('#search-text', 10000, function (err, el) {
el.sendKeys(wd.SPECIAL_KEYS.Return);
});
})
})
.waitForElementByCss('.item', 20000, function elementCb(err, el) {
if (err) throw err;
should.exist(el);
})
.title(function (err, title) {
if (title.indexOf(site.keys.searchFound) == -1) {
return next('Title not match');
}
return next(err);
})
}
function searchTest() {
try {
actualSearchTest(function (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold) {
searchTest();
}
else {
return done(err);
}
});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
searchTest();
else return done(err);
}
}
searchTest();

tests.code:
function itemClick(done) {
var tries = 0;
function actualPaginationTest(next) {
driver.chain()
.elementByCss('.btn-next', function(err, btnEl){
btnEl.elementByCss('a', function(err, btnA){
if (err) btnEl.click();
else btnA.click();
})
})
.waitForElementByCss('.btn-previous', 10000)
.url(function(err, url){
if (url.indexOf(site.keys.pagination) == -1) {
return next('Title not match');
}
return next(err);
})
}
function paginationTest() {
try {
actualPaginationTest(function (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold) {
paginationTest();
}
else {
return done(err);
}
});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
paginationTest();
else return done(err);
}
}
paginationTest();

allPasses.code:
function sectionsClick(done) {
var tries = 0;
function actualSearchTest(next) {
driver.chain()
.get(site.urls.live)
.elementByCss('.search-focus', function touchSearch(err, search) {
if (err) throw err;
search.flick(1, 1, 0, function flickCb(err) {
if (err) throw err;
driver.elementByCss('#search-text', 10000, function (err, el) {
el.sendKeys(wd.SPECIAL_KEYS.Return);
});
})
})
.waitForElementByCss('.item', 20000, function elementCb(err, el) {
if (err) throw err;
should.exist(el);
})
.title(function (err, title) {
if (title.indexOf(site.keys.searchFound) == -1) {
return next('Title not match');
}
return next(err);
})
}
function searchTest() {
try {
actualSearchTest(function (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold) {
searchTest();
}
else {
return done(err);
}
});
} catch (err) {
if (err && tries++ < tries_threshold)
searchTest();
else return done(err);
}
}
searchTest();
